### Step 1: Presigned URL 발급
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/images/upload-url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageType": "THUMBNAIL",
  "contentType": "image/png",
  "contentLength": 10362,
  "originalFileName": "bitcoin.png"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("uploadUrl", response.body.uploadUrl);
%}

### Step 2: Presigned URL로 MinIO에 직접 업로드 (PUT)
# Content-Type은 Step 1에서 지정한 값과 반드시 일치해야 함
PUT {{uploadUrl}}
Content-Type: image/png

< ./bitcoin.png

### Register Product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sellerId": 3,
  "categoryId": 12,
  "productName": "갤럭시 S25",
  "descriptionHtml": "<p>최신 플래그십</p>",
  "brand": "Samsung",
  "manufacturer": "Samsung Electronics",
  "salesStartDate": "2026-05-10T00:00:00",
  "attributes": { "resolution": 1280, "pencil_required": false },
  "skus": [
    { "skuCode": "GS25-BLK-256", "options": {"color":"BLACK","storage":256}, "price": 1500000, "stockQuantity": 100 },
    { "skuCode": "GS25-WHT-256", "options": {"color":"WHITE","storage":256}, "price": 1500000, "stockQuantity": 80 }
  ],
  "images": [
    {
      "imageType": "THUMBNAIL",
      "imagePath": "product-images/products/thumbnail/2026/05/ff6774bc-7baa-4e08-a41a-ec94b5e3027c.png",
      "displayOrder": 0,
      "storageKey": "products/thumbnail/2026/05/ff6774bc-7baa-4e08-a41a-ec94b5e3027c.png",
      "fileSize": 10362,
      "mimeType": "image/png"
    }
  ]
}

### ADD Skus
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/1/skus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skus": [
    {"skuCode": "SKU-PROD-1", "price": 100000, "stockQuantity": 200}
  ]
}

### Deactivate Skus
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/1/skus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skuCode": "SKU-PROD-1"
}
